title: Winamp 5.5
description:
Winamp 5.5

This latest version  of Winamp is a free multimedia player made by Nullsoft. It supports numerous audio and video formats. It also plays streamed 
video and audio content, both live and recorded, authored worldwide. It has an extremely customizable media library,
and allows you to rip and burn your favorite music CDs. Winamp has thousands of skins and plug-ins that allow you to change 
the look-and-feel of the player, as well as add new features. The player also has access to thousands of free songs, 
videos and online radio stations from SHOUTcast Radio and AOL Radio with XM.

Unzip or unrar, then install this basic version without burning or ripping features. Then read txt-  files instructions to register application to pro version.
